1
00:00:03,590 --> 00:00:04,710
What do you think?

2
00:00:04,710 --> 00:00:07,260
Yeah, it looks good.

3
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:09,220
Now for the lipstick...

4
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:12,850
This is the one I usually use.
Do you want to try it?

5
00:00:14,720 --> 00:00:16,680
Huh? You're not a germaphobe, are you?

6
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:19,060
No, that's not it... Um...
That's not what I meant.

7
00:00:19,060 --> 00:00:21,940
But it's probably better
to have your own lipstick, right?

8
00:00:22,610 --> 00:00:24,190
Want to go buy one?

9
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:33,280
- Ooh, it's a new release...
- This one over here looks nice.

10
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:35,160
- I'm interested.
- Mmm.

11
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:37,450
This shade is pretty natural.

12
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:43,130
It's not exactly "cute,"
but it's a very flattering color.

13
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:46,710
Oh... Sorry, Yuki.
Can I use the restroom real quick?

14
00:00:46,710 --> 00:00:48,550
Sure, I'll just look around here.

15
00:00:58,350 --> 00:01:01,730
(If I had something like this,
maybe I could be a little better?)

16
00:01:03,940 --> 00:01:08,940
(I ended up buying it...
I'll just give it to him as a thank-you gift for today.)

17
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,290
(Wh-what?!
Who... Who is that?!)

18
00:01:17,290 --> 00:01:19,040
(Could it be... Yuki's girlfriend?!)
